          item: "ae2:portable_item_cell_1k",
          consume_items: "true"
        }
      ],
      description: ["  The Portable Cell is AE2's version of a backpack, offering a much larger portable storage solution than most backpacks, bags, etc. available from other mods.  The only downside is that you have to recharge it occasionally."],
      icon: "ae2:portable_item_cell_1k",
      dependencies: ["0200000001580000"],
